data.description: Plenty to offer in Town!! Privately situated on corner lot in the small town of Parsons, this cute 3BR 2 BA brick home has unique features! Completely fenced in on a gorgeous lushly landscaped lot, this home features a cute well appointed kitchen w/granite counter tops, all appliances, island, breakfast nook. Plantation shutters in every room, and hardwood throughout. Extra large back BR serves as a den or BR, vaulted ceiling, fireplace,french doors out to nice patio, storage building. Call Anne 7315497531
